channel.title: Eurodancer Sketch - Azure Onyxscore
channel.description:
It's been, how long? 12 years since DJ Mangoo released the famous Eurodancer which totally didn't make me go into tears when I've heard this song. Some of you are too young to remember this before Geometry Dash popularized it. This song was released back when MySpace was still a thing.
Feel free to remix it however you desire, there's no deadline for it, just remix whenever. Just remember to post your projects here.
;-)
